"1/4 cup extra-virgin olive oil, plus more for drizzling","2 heads garlic, cloves separated but not peeled","3 cloves garlic, minced","1 tablespoon minced rosemary, plus 3 sprigs","1 tablespoon minced thyme","1  bone-in leg of lamb, aitch bone removed","  Salt","  Freshly ground pepper","1  large sweet onion, cut into 1/2-inch-thick wedges","2  large carrots, cut on the diagonal 1/2 inch thick","2  large celery ribs, cut on the diagonal 1/2 inch thick"